<div><h2 id="description">Description</h2>
<div class="description"><div class="jqm-loaddialog-page"><p>Shows a wait dialog to indicate some long running work.</p>
</div></div>
<h2 id="dependencies">Dependencies</h2>
<ul class="dependencies"><li><code ng:non-bindable=""><a href="#/api/ng.$rootElement">$rootElement</a></code>
</li>
<li><code ng:non-bindable=""><a href="#/api/ng.$rootScope">$rootScope</a></code>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="usage">Usage</h2>
<div class="usage"><pre class="prettyprint linenums">$loadDialog();</pre>
</div>
<div class="member method"><h2 id="methods">Methods</h2>
<ul class="methods"><li><h3 id="methods_hide">hide()</h3>
<div class=""><div class="jqm-loaddialog-hide-page"><p>Restores the dialog state before the show function was called.</p>
</div></div>
</li>
<li><h3 id="methods_show">show(message, callback)</h3>
<div class="show"><div class="jqm-loaddialog-show-page"><p>Opens the wait dialog and shows the given message (if existing).
If the user clicks on the wait dialog the given callback is called.
This can be called even if the dialog is currently showing. It will
then change the message and revert back to the last message when
the hide function is called.</p>
</div><h5 id="methods_show_parameters">Parameters</h5><table class="variables-matrix table table-bordered table-striped"><thead><tr><th>Param</th><th>Type</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>message <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-string">string</a></td><td><div class="jqm-loaddialog-show-page"><p>The message to be shown when the wait dialog is displayed.</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>callback <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-function">function</a></td><td><div class="jqm-loaddialog-show-page"><p>The Callback that is executed when the wait dialog is clicked.</p>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
</li>
<li><h3 id="methods_waitfor">waitFor(promise, message)</h3>
<div class="waitfor"><div class="jqm-loaddialog-waitfor-page"><p>Shows the dialog as long as the given promise runs. Shows the given message
if defined.</p>
</div><h5 id="methods_waitfor_parameters">Parameters</h5><table class="variables-matrix table table-bordered table-striped"><thead><tr><th>Param</th><th>Type</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>promise</td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-promise">Promise</a></td><td><div class="jqm-loaddialog-waitfor-page"><p>The Promise.</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>message <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-string">string</a></td><td><div class="jqm-loaddialog-waitfor-page"><p>The message to be show.</p>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
</li>
<li><h3 id="methods_waitforwithcancel">waitForWithCancel(The, cancelData, message)</h3>
<div class="waitforwithcancel"><div class="jqm-loaddialog-waitforwithcancel-page"><p>Same as jqm.$loadDialog#waitFor, but rejects the promise with the given
cancelData when the user clicks on the wait dialog.</p>
