</div></td></tr><tr><td>cancelData</td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-object">*</a></td><td><div class="jqm-loaddialog-waitforwithcancel-page"><p>To reject the promise with.</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>message <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-string">string</a></td><td><div class="jqm-loaddialog-waitforwithcancel-page"><p>The message to be show.</p>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
</li>
</ul>
